<p>The already trendy delicacy has now gone absolutely viral thanks to the BTS member&rsquo;s recent visit to a spot famous for nut-based desserts, La Pistacherie. In turn, it became one of the most talked-about moments from this year&rsquo;s Paris Fashion Week. V truly knows how to make it all about him, and we can&rsquo;t get enough of it!</p>
