<p><strong>Lee Chae Min and Ryu Da In&rsquo;s love story progresses</strong><br />
Speaking to SPOTV News, he emphasized how his personal life does not affect his professional one, and instead only encourages him to do better. &ldquo;Rather than being pressured by being in a public relationship, it gives me more passion to immerse myself in the role.&rdquo; He added that they do not exclusively discuss their projects.</p>

