<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>What is KDOL?</strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">KDOL is a mobile app that tracks and ranks K-pop idols based entirely on fan votes collected in real time. The application is unlike charts that are influenced by sales or media appearances. It provides a platform where international fans can directly support their favorite artists through daily voting.&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">Users from the U.S., South Korea, Japan, Southeast Asia, and other parts of the world participate daily, giving the platform a wide global reach. Votes are tallied by the app daily, weekly, and monthly, with totals locked in every day at midnight KST. Top-ranking idols are featured in KDOL&rsquo;s Hall of Fame, making it a key space for tracking fan engagement and global popularity.</p>
