<p style="text-align:justify"><a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/extraordinary-you-star-rowoon-to-enlist-in-military-in-july-ahead-of-the-murky-stream-release-know-estimated-discharge-date-1389611">Rowoon </a>had been preparing to join as an active-duty soldier. But the standard pre-enlistment check, conducted under the guidelines of the Military Manpower Administration (MMA), raised concerns that require further medical review. As a result, <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/jung-hae-in-and-rowoon-confirmed-for-special-cameos-in-spring-of-youth-starring-ha-yoo-joon-and-park-ji-hoo-report-1383582">Rowoon </a>received a Grade 7 classification. It is a designation that mandates a re-examination.</p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>Rowoon receives Grade 7 in pre-enlistment exam</strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">According to FNC, the MMA began conducting pre-enlistment physical examinations two weeks ahead of each scheduled enlistment starting this month. During <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/academy-awards-2025-blackpinks-lisa-stuns-in-floor-length-tuxedo-rowoon-shimmers-in-black-suit-1375405">Rowoon</a>&rsquo;s check-up, he was issued a Grade 7 result. It signifies uncertainty regarding his medical eligibility and defers enlistment until further assessment.</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">The agency explained that due to the result, Rowoon&rsquo;s enlistment has been postponed. He has already filed an appeal and will undergo a reassessment in early August.</p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>Rowoon&rsquo;s commitment to serve remains firm</strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">Despite the delay, Rowoon has expressed a clear intention to fulfill his national duty. FNC added, &ldquo;He hopes to confirm that there are no issues with fulfilling his mandatory service and to enlist as an active-duty soldier as soon as possible,&rdquo; as quoted by Soompi.</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">The agency clarified that the reason for the re-examination involves private medical information. FNC added, &ldquo;We are unable to disclose the details.&rdquo; They asked for the public&rsquo;s understanding.</p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>Fans praise Rowoon&rsquo;s responsible approach</strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">FNC concluded its statement by assuring fans that they will provide further updates once Rowoon&#39;s new enlistment schedule is confirmed. As news broke about the postponement, social media platforms gets flooded with heartfelt messages from fans across the globe.</p>

